            <thetext>It seems that at least at Mac OS the combination &quot;Ctrl+Enter&quot; should insert a simple linebreak instead of a new paragraph. We should support this behaviour for Safari browsers at all platforms since both combination (&quot;Ctrl+Enter&quot; and &quot;Shift+Enter&quot;) should end up in a simple linebreak.

This one seems fixable, but for &quot;Shift+Enter&quot; we need to wait for a fix from the Webkit team. See Bug #2317 for details</thetext>
